Description:
The Desire of All Dandenong!!!
Enviably situated in the coveted Metro Village Estate, the immediate appeal of this modern residence is more than matched by the spacious interiors that brilliantly showcase the home's allure with a contemporary floorplan. This immaculate haven has an inviting Open Plan Living with ample kitchen cabinets and pantries, a separate dining area and a spacious second living area.
The Master bedroom is carefully tucked away on the upper floor with an extra-large Walk in Robe and a double vanity Ensuite. Upper floor also presents 3 good sized bedrooms with spacious WIRs, with 2 separate toilet, powder room downstairs and a main bathroom featuring a bathtub.
A remote-controlled double garage and a private easy maintenance courtyard is ideal for families. A delightful surprise package, it also includes ducted heating and evaporative cooling throughout, air-conditioning on the master bedroom with four extra linden space for your storage.
Desirably situated opposite the Dandenong Station, within short walking distance to the retail precinct like Dandenong Plaza and Market, local businesses, pre-schools, primary schools, high schools and an abundance of multicultural eateries. Commuting to the city is made easy with Eastlink and Princes Highway close by and Public Transport is within reach.
Please Note
* Full Contact Details including Phone Number required when you make an enquiry.
* Photo ID required at all open for inspections.

Description:
soldAS - My signs are everywhere - SOLD BY DINESH RAGHU
Backing onto parklands, this well-maintained, single storey family home offers elegant interiors, easy-care outdoor spaces and an excellent location.
The flexible layout boasts three spacious living zones; at the front of the home, a formal living or theatre room, in the heart of the home, a generous open plan kitchen, meals and family area and to the rear, a third living space well suited as a rumpus room, playroom or home office. Continue outside and imagine the family barbeques and festive celebrations to be held in the entertainment pergola with lovely timber decking.
Also on offer are three bedrooms; a master bedroom with walk in robe and private ensuite plus two additional robed bedrooms that share a family bathroom. A long list of extras complete this spacious and comfortable casa; a walk in pantry, double garage, timber style flooring, stone benchtops, glass splashback, high ceilings, LED downlights, ducted heating, reverse cycle air conditioner, back to base alarm, security shutters, NBN connectivity and plenty of storage cupboards.
If you’re heading out simply follow Dandenong Creek and walking trails into the heart of Dandenong CBD and enjoy brilliant local amenities such as the Dandenong Markets and Plaza, restaurants, parks, schools and train station.
• Elegant, single storey family home packed with extras plus rear yard access to parklands
• Three robed bedrooms, two bathrooms, laundry and plenty of storage space
• Gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, glass splashback and walk in pantry
• Timber style flooring, high ceilings, LED downlights, ducted heating, reverse cycle air conditioner, back to base alarm, security shutters and NBN connectivity
• Low maintenance gardens, alfresco with timber decking and double garage

Description:
Spacious Modern Apartment in Secure Complex and Prime Location
Live or invest in this recently built apartment. Located on the top floor of the building, offering undisrupted greenery views and one of the best floor layouts with almost 100sqm in size.
Upon entering, residents will be greeted by a nice welcoming hallway that creates that instant relaxed feeling. Large windows throughout the unit maximize the vast open style living and dining area outlook, allowing residents to turn the home into a multipurpose space without feeling restricted.
The contemporary kitchen is completed with four burner gas cooktops, stainless steel appliances and tile flooring.
Also, include two queen-size bedrooms both with B.I.Rs and an ensuite in the master bedroom providing residents with the utmost privacy. A second bathroom or guest powder is strategically located just after the entrance.
Another focal point of this unit is its large balcony that can easily accommodate your favourite BBQ sessions or brilliant balcony garden inspirations. Split system heating/ cooling, intercom and secure underground parking space also comes with this fantastic property.
Situated within close proximity of Dandenong's hot spots such as Dandenong Market, Dandenong Plaza and a growing number of eateries and retailers.
Educational institutes such as Dandenong High and Primary School as well as bus stops and Dandenong Station are all within short reach.

Description:
A trendy renovated apartment in central Dandenong
Enter through 6 McFarlane Crescent Dandenong
So close the Central Dandenong that you can see if from the back windows, this first floor apartment has also been completely renovated making a must see for both occupiers and investors.
A great lifestyle choice, this apartment define low maintenance living when you can walk to Dandenong Market, the plaza shopping centre and all of the areas local eateries and cultural amenities. Presenting better than new, the home has been freshly painted and fully re-wired with floating floors, low voltage lighting and window furnishings adding to its appeal. The living area with electric heater is sun lit and adjoins the trendy kitchen with bold red tiled splashback, stainless cooking appliances and an included meals area. Both bedrooms feature built in wardrobes and there's also a combined bathroom/laundry with floor to ceiling tiles and a separate toilet with its own striking tile feature. There's also security intercom entry and a covered car space on title.
**PHOTO ID REQUIRED FOR ALL OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS**

Description:
2 Bedroom Unit With Private Yard
Set back from the road, this complex is so private that from the street you are not aware.
From the separate entry hall to the lounge room with timber blinds and on to the clean, spacious kitchen/meals area, this property feels more like a small house than a unit.
The kitchen has a cooktop, underbench oven and a dishwasher and the bench overlooks the meals area that will accommodate your dining suite.
There is a private rear yard with access to the single lock up garage. Easy walk back to Dandenong train station, CBD and more.
Currently leased on a monthly basis and the tenant would love to stay or vacant possession available.
AFFORDABLE LIVING!

Description:
Your Wish Has Been Granted!
Mere moments away from completion, this contemporary townhouse is your chance to own and enjoy everything brand new and just for you. Positioned in the heart of thriving Dandenong, this premium location offers both primary and secondary schools within less than 1km, convenient shopping at Dandenong Markets and Plaza, a selection of local parks and reserves as well as easy transport options with nearby bus services, Dandenong Train Station, Princes Highway and the Monash Freeway.
Street frontage and a modern facade create great first impressions and inside continues to deliver with high ceilings, bright interiors and quality throughout. On the ground floor, an open plan living and dining area connects with the private courtyard. The kitchen beams brightly with white finishes including stone benchtops, satin cabinetry and a tiled splashback as well as quality appliances to be added upon completion. A laundry and guest powder room complete the downstairs layout whilst upstairs accommodates two bedrooms with built in robes, a central bathroom, retreat area and balcony overlooking the locale. Enjoy personalised heating and cooling control with a reverse cycle air conditioner in the living zone as well as one in each bedroom.
Soon to be completed with landscaping, the outdoor space also includes a covered patio, water tank and single garage with handy internal access. A perfect match for first home buyers, investors or even downsizers looking to leave behind the demanding maintenance of an aging property, this brand new residence is sure to be a market favourite.
Call us today and get set to be impressed with this terrific townhouse in a premium position!

Description:
Pick Me Up or Push Me Down!
This 2-bedroom plus study (or 3rd bedroom) home is ripe for renovation and presents some inspired new owners with a number of challenges or the option of knocking the property down and starting over again!
Situated in a quiet court, with no passing traffic could be ideal for a family with children as well. This home just needs someone realise the full potential it presents and act on this vision. With the lack of flat, rectangular blocks in Melbourne, this property is competitively priced to attract a buyer who would endeavour to rediscover this homes treasures or simply demolish and build your dream home or the possibility of a two-house site (STCA). Plus, with reliable tenants on a month by month agreement, there’s plenty of flexibility there too.
With a wide street frontage, there’s heaps of easy access to the rear of the property and with the convenience of transport, shops and schools close by, this home has property has a plethora of options.
